{"type":"text","timestamp":1775882223200,"sessionID":"ses_2852d14c5ffemqmGQLLUOKGbvL","part":{"id":"prt_d7ad43a41001ijbKB1TvKm2ncg","messageID":"msg_d7ad39237001KkP4Vbx8l67vWQ","sessionID":"ses_2852d14c5ffemqmGQLLUOKGbvL","type":"text","text":"Looking at the prompt, I need to review and update the delta-spec.md for AR-019 to ensure it aligns with the base spec (`deployment/client-go.md`) which defines the `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API group with `AgentRuntime` and `CodeInterpreter` types.\n\nThe existing delta-spec.md references different API groups. Let me update it to be consistent with the client-go base spec:","time":{"start":1775882223197,"end":1775882223197}}}
